      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/card/task_001/scope_drift",
      "@type": "asbval:ScopeDriftAssertion",
      "asbval:drift_notes": [
        "The candidate task card describes a web service availability/HTTP connectivity check task, which is entirely outside the scope of the paper. The paper is a computational biology/mass spectrometry methods paper focused on algorithmic improvements and accuracy benchmarking of molDiscovery as a standalone tool.",
        "The paper does mention GitHub repository links for results (e.g., 'https://github.com/mohimanilab/molDiscovery') but does not describe deployment of a web service or document any HTTP endpoint for molDiscovery.",
        "The task card appears to conflate the existence of a software tool (molDiscovery) with the existence of a web service interface, which is not supported by the paper."
      ],
      "asbval:n_drift_notes": 3,
      "asbval:target_artifact_id": "task_001",
      "asbval:target_artifact_kind": "card",
